rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0010
rows.name: ...You came.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0020
rows.name: There is no longer any meaning to this fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0030
rows.name: And still your efforts to resist me do not cease.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0040
rows.name: How long...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0050
rows.name: For how long will you displease me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0060
rows.name: Give Al back to us, Void.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0070
rows.name: Now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0080
rows.name: In mere moments, I will effect my escape.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0090
rows.name: I will win.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0100
rows.name: There is a limit to the time you have left.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0110
rows.name: You need not waste it on this meaningless struggle.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0120
rows.name: ...Look.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0130
rows.name: The cores are charging up gradually.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0140
rows.name: If they really are Void's power source...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0150
rows.name: then as soon as they're done,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0160
rows.name: he'll use them, and try to make a break for it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0170
rows.name: We have to act now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0180
rows.name: We need Alâ€”[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0190
rows.name: he's our only way out of this mess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0200
rows.name: Elma... About that spear we activated...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0210
rows.name: I'm detecting a lot of energy being stored within.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0220
rows.name: And I mean a LOT, a lot.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0230
rows.name:
I think if we gave it a good whack,
all that energy would be released...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0240
rows.name: ...And Void would take the brunt?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0250
rows.name: Right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0260
rows.name:
And even if he didn't, it should work to
put the breaks on his power.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0270
rows.name: Got it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0280
rows.name: You hear that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0290
rows.name: Going for the spear will give us an edge in this fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0300
rows.name: Keep that in mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs33800110_MSG0310
rows.name: Go![ST:wait ]
